thinking_machine: TM\: Left. Right. Left. Right.
thinking_machine: TM\: Move your legs as I instruct.
thinking_machine: TM\: Look ou-
You trip and drop him. The Thinking Machine hits the ground and breaks in two.
You look up for the first time in years, and as your eyes shift focus for the first time in as long, you realize that you do not recognize anything you see.